{"type":"message","id":"6bed26ae","parentId":"56696a1a","timestamp":"2026-04-01T10:30:38.073Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Wed 2026-04-01 18:30 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 执行盘后复盘+邮件报告流程：\n\n1. **数据获取阶段**：\n   - 使用SSH/SCP从云服务器118.89.118.199拉取文件：\n     - E:/Quant/Datas/daily_result.json\n     - E:/Quant/Datas/positions.json\n   - 读取本地的plan.json（预测vs实际对比）\n   - 读取历史报告_index.json（防重复犯错）\n\n2. **因子有效性追踪分析**：\n   - 读取strategies/reports/factor_tracking.json\n   - 对比今日每只股票的选股因子表现\n   - 判断因子有效性：PE/PB分位、机构资金流向、ROE趋势、换手率异动等\n   - 更新factor_tracking.json：days_above/days_below、avg_return_when_signal、hit_rate、notes\n   - 生成因子有效性排行榜：最有效因子TOP3 + 最失效因子TOP3\n\n3. **新闻回溯分析**：\n   - 检查持仓股当日涨跌幅>5%或触发止损/止盈的个股\n   - 用web_search搜索相关新闻：\"股票代码/名称 + 新闻\" 和行业新闻\n   - 分析新闻与涨跌的因果关系，记录到因子追踪notes\n\n4. **复盘报告生成**：\n   - 今日盈亏总览\n   - 个股表现明细（异常个股附新闻分析）\n   - 因子有效性排行榜\n   - 教训总结（对比_index.json）\n   - 明日关注点\n\n5. **邮件发送**：\n   - 使用Gmail SMTP发送到l1cheeyuan@163.com\n   - 发件箱：yuanlynch@gmail.com\n   - SMTP: smtp.gmail.com:587\n   - 使用现有的邮件脚本或创建新报告"}],"timestamp":1775039438072}}
{"type":"message","id":"ffb918ff","parentId":"6bed26ae","timestamp":"2026-04-01T10:30:45.716Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me break down this task into phases:\n\n1. First, I need to fetch data from the cloud server via SSH/SCP\n2. Read local files (plan.json, historical reports)\n3. Factor tracking analysis\n4. News analysis for abnormal stocks\n5. Generate review report\n6. Send email\n\nLet me start by reading the necessary skill files and local data, then SSH to fetch remote files.\n\nLet me begin with parallel tasks:\n- Read local plan.json\n- Read historical report index\n- Read factor tracking\n- SSH to fetch remote files","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"开始执行盘后复盘流程。先并行获取所有数据源。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d7597eb8ed7c4c409743e788","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace-chairong/strategies/plan.json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7d5706f5bc5348168df658a6","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace-chairong/strategies/reports/factor_tracking.json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_93db3ff1abe74b789a9f6a31","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace-chairong/strategies/reports/"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e8eadc49258d427ea06f33ec","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace-chairong && cat .env.local 2>/dev/null | grep SSH_PASSWORD || echo \"NO_ENV_LOCAL\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-customb2","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":33543,"output":366,"cacheRead":4583,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38492,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775039438073}}
